1. Populate ticket_created_at


=VLOOKUP(A2, ticket!E:F, 2, FALSE)

OR

=XLOOKUP(A2, ticket!E:E, ticket!B:B)

2a. Same day created & closed

=COUNTIFS(
created_date_range, date,
closed_date_range, date,
outlet_range, outlet_id
)

2b. Same hour

Create helper:

=TEXT(created_at,"yyyy-mm-dd hh")
=TEXT(closed_at,"yyyy-mm-dd hh")

Then:

=COUNTIFS(created_hour, X, closed_hour, X)